<h2>Summary of quality attributes for PolarSys projects</h2>

<div class="row">

  <div class="col-sm-7">

    <p>This document gathers the quality attributes computed on all analysed projects, summarises them, and proposes a transverse perspective on the projects ratings. Its main purpose is to help users  understand the differences between projects and get hints as how to improve their practices.</p>

    <p>This is a <em>dynamically generated</em> document: it takes as input the <code>attributes.csv</code> file generated by the dashboard, then outputs a summary and plots the values for all projects. In this very case, <!--rinline projects.vol --> projects with a total of <!-- rinline ncol(projects) - 1 --> quality attributes have been analysed.</p>

