<h3 id="metrics_scm">Main quality characteristics</h3>

<h4 id="attr_maturity">Maturity</h4>

<p>The overall rating of a project is defined as its <em>maturity</em>. It is defined as the mean of its subcharacteristics: Ecosystem, Process, Product, and reflects the conformance of the project to the set of quality requirements established for the measurement process.</p>

